value.string: This code block fetches the "Billing Type" and "Billing Amount" based on Business logic
Check if window containing Billing table is loaded.
Check if Billing table is loaded
Get Billing table and assign it to a table variable
If Billing table is not yet loaded, try after 15 Seconds.
Check for each row where Description and src / effective date match
Description should be "CHANGES MADE PER UNDERWRITIN"
Src / effective date should match with Input effective date
